{"LanguageCode":"en","SurahData":{"Chapter":107,"Index":"107","Name":"Al-Ma'un","TranslatedName":"The Small Kindnesses","ArabicName":"سُوْرَةُ الْمَاعُوْنِ","Revelation":"Mecca","RevelationOrder":17,"HasBismillah":true,"VerseCount":7,"SajdaCount":0,"JuzStart":30,"JuzEnd":30,"VerseStart":6198,"VerseEnd":6204,"ManzilStart":7,"ManzilEnd":7,"RukuStart":549,"RukuEnd":549,"MaqraStart":240,"MaqraEnd":240,"PageStart":602,"PageEnd":602},"Summaries":["<p>7 Verses in 1 section. Religion means social service, helping the poor and needy. The Surah tells us that the true belief in God and the last day create a kind and compassionate character.</p>"],"Verses":[{"Verse":1,"Text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","End":"١"},{"Verse":2,"Text":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","End":"٢"},{"Verse":3,"Text":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","End":"٣"},{"Verse":4,"Text":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","End":"٤"},{"Verse":5,"Text":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","End":"٥"},{"Verse":6,"Text":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","End":"٦"},{"Verse":7,"Text":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","End":"٧"}],"Translations":[{"LanguageCode":"eng","Language":"English","Name":"eng-mustafakhattabg","Author":"Mustafa Khattab God Edition","Source":"","Direction":"ltr","Translations":[{"Verse":1,"Text":"Have you seen the one who denies the ˹final˺ Judgment"},{"Verse":2,"Text":"That is the one who repulses the orphan"},{"Verse":3,"Text":"and does not encourage the feeding of the poor"},{"Verse":4,"Text":"So woe to those ˹hypocrites˺ who pray"},{"Verse":5,"Text":"yet are unmindful of their prayers"},{"Verse":6,"Text":"those who ˹only˺ show off"},{"Verse":7,"Text":"and refuse to give ˹even the simplest˺ aid"}]}]}